    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏QQ群：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >372623190</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>反馈&amp;联系邮箱：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><a href=\"mailto:weiqianyangwenwen@126.com\">weiqianyangwenwen@126.com</a></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战国游侠模拟器！有丰富的主支线及DLC内容，游戏中你出身布衣，以战国游侠之姿纵横于乱世，最终成为封君乃至至高无上的君王，平乱世开太平。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏背景：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 公元前403年，“三家分晋”，中国历史进入了战乱纷争的战国时代。原本只是一介草民的你，却被卷入了一场巨大的阴谋之中，被亲情、友情与仇恨交织裹挟的你，能否生存下去，并为万民带来安宁？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏内容概述：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>驰骋于广阔的九州大地</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏构建了以中原为中心的大地图，采用战略大地图+分场景小地图的方式呈现，玩家可游历于一方广大的天地之间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/89fb70db5d1e40c4950f896743bcef65.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/1a14f9ca36e878f712f7989fa7a76a3e.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/c3d0ba341cd758b58c29cb69044c8ad9.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/a247d28f73e9f9647a8d8d4d246435d5.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/98f20f31c9911dce92409f0771908051.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富多样的主线及支线任务系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏由主线剧情+支线任务构成，随着主线剧情的推进，玩家所扮演的角色将会展开一场惊心动魄的旅途，并最终揭开一段鲜为人知的往事，支线剧情则有更多的选择与自由度，形形色色的小故事与遭遇，让一路的旅途增添了丰富的的趣味。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/a6262eb6f75b3e1b67e0df536a859139.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/b28f72efdc8ed62214022dc59860d633.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/f7e5f3e0b6be17fd75e33c4a796c5ad7.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/f6354f34f20afb11f1ceec707df36794.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>贸易与跑商</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“天下熙熙皆为利来，天下攘攘皆为利往”，游戏中商人几乎无处不在，他们正等待着与你达成交易。游戏中玩家通过战斗能获得不少物资，将剩余的物资卖予商贩，可获取钱财，逐渐积累起属于自己的大量财富。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/6892bdba37f8a1bbf754aaf76f2d738c.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>组建自己的卫队（私甲）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着玩家爵位的提升，也逐渐拥有了招募属于自己的私甲的资格，尤其在同时拥有了大量的钱财之后，组建忠心于自己的私甲便成为了可能，玩家通过在各地招募兵勇，并带领他们冲锋陷阵，逐渐壮大自己的队伍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/f04f9485aebb7b22d32032e7793fe65b.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>修身治国平天下</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏后期，角色可以拥有自己的封邑，并以此为基础开拓自己的领地，以致最终成为一国之君，参与逐鹿天下，最终一统乱世。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/f2876450a8f4f8609f7e06e8f0f21c5f.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/b066a73fb0fd683565b85baa3c68e30f.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/e6c59f18b384d68e9b4826fe4bac922a.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/f01954dd076181c0ac0b61f7963bfacc.avif?t=1769932338\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>DLC相关</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏目前已经已经有两个DLC，分别为“小国寡民”、“礼崩乐坏&quot;。为表诚意，<strong>我们决定所有购买了游戏的玩家，都可以免费获取DLC</strong>！<strong>将来新开发的DLC，所有玩家也能自动免费获得！</strong>游戏采用半开放式的开发框架，理论上后续可以在基本功能的基础上，持续开发更多的不同剧情的DLC供大家体验！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>周王畿DLC大地图图示（网页端可点开放大查看）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/adfaa7d4a43d1aafe5bb9df631e66cfc.avif?t=1769932338\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras_big/adfaa7d4a43d1aafe5bb9df631e66cfc.webp?t=1769932338 width=1560 height=1560 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>秦国DLC大地图图示（网页端可点开放大查看）</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras/966dcb891c9d598b063eb337e67a546b.avif?t=1769932338\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001460/extras_big/966dcb891c9d598b063eb337e67a546b.webp?t=1769932338 width=1560 height=1560 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >后记：忆战国之世，兵戈交接，血流漂杵，骨骸填于沟壑，万民饱受涂炭之苦。此乱世之中，众王侯将相虽显赫一时，身后名尚为世所称赞者，寥寥而已。今之众人，每追思先者，虽愚夫愚妇，亦为献身救民救世而赴义者感怀垂泪，而以罔民虐民者为仇寇。私者虽得志于一时一世，然百世之后，自有公论。故谚曰：民为贵。又曰：民者，神之主也。以史为鉴，可知兴替，岂可不慎哉？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
